---
title: Bacon, Carrot & Lentil Soup plus Garlic Toasts & Parmesan
description: This smoky lentil and carrot soup is packed with smoky bacon and infused with herbaceous thyme—our fresh spin on hearty French-style lentil soup. Sprinkle those lucky bowls with umami-rich Parmesan cheese just before serving, and serve with crisp, buttery garlic ciabatta toasts for dipping.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66ccac7586da4647f4e3676a-6541330d.jpeg
